  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the safety and effectiveness Percutaneous Transluminal Angioplasty(PTA)
      using Drug-Coated Balloons for the treatment of Superficial Femoral and popliteal peripheral
      Artery disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
